      {
        "purpose": "transcribing",
        "value": "権少参事 本多時雨平藤原政醇・稲葉助五郎越智通安・丹羽次郎藤原履信・斯波蕃源正邦・岡島喜太郎藤原一式・中川甚六源克由・北川亥之作・不破亮三郎藤原貞順・澤邨恒三藤原武成"
      },
      {
        "purpose": "modern_jp_reading",
        "value": "権少参事（ごんしょうさんじ）— 本多時雨平ほか九名の名簿"
      },
      {
        "purpose": "english_translation",
        "value": "Provisional Junior Councillors (gon-shō-sanji) — a named roster: Honda Shigurehei, Inaba Sukegorō, Niwa Jirō, Shiba Shigeru, Okajima Kitarō, Nakagawa Jinroku, Kitagawa Inosaku, Fuwa Ryōzaburō, and Sawamura Tsunezō. Each name is given with its formal clan name (藤原・源・越智)."
      },
      {
        "purpose": "extracted_value",
        "value": "9-name roster"
      },
      {
        "purpose": "identifying",
        "value": "権少参事"
